OL,3,CWhy the path to Westminster is not so
OL,4,Csimple for Andy Burnham
OL,6,FThe issue has always been that there
OL,7,Fisn't a clear route for him to return
OL,8,Fto Westminster, but now, with the by-
OL,9,Felection in Gorton and Denton pending,
OL,10,Fa path has opened up.
OL,12,FThe seat sits in Burnham's political
OL,13,Fbackyard and the vacancy has emerged
OL,14,Fthrough an MP stepping aside on health
OL,15,Fgrounds rather than any choreographed
OL,16,Fmanoeuvre.
