OL,3,CWhy the path to Westminster is not so
OL,4,Csimple for Andy Burnham
OL,6,FIt is therefore an organic opening and
OL,7,Fnot one that has been manufactured,
OL,8,Fthus providing a realistic route back
OL,9,Fto the Commons for the man who left
OL,10,FLondon in 2017 to become the mayor of
OL,11,FGreater Manchester.
OL,13,FAlthough Burnham has not made his
OL,14,Fintentions clear, the path is anything
OL,15,Fbut straightforward.
OL,17,FLabour's all-powerful National
OL,18,FExecutive Committee (NEC) will have to
OL,19,Fgive explicit approval before a
OL,20,Fdirectly elected mayor can seek a
OL,21,FWestminster nomination.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
