OL,3,CWhy the path to Westminster is not so
OL,4,Csimple for Andy Burnham
OL,6,FThis potentially allows those within
OL,7,Fthe party's leadership to block
OL,8,FBurnham from standing.
OL,10,FI've heard from multiple members of
OL,11,Fthe NEC about several different
OL,12,Fmethods that could be used to make
OL,13,Fthis happen. An all-woman or ethnic
OL,14,Fminority shortlist is one I've heard
OL,15,Fmentioned. This would address issues
OL,16,Fwithin the current makeup of the
OL,17,FParliamentary Labour Party - but
OL,18,Fultimately stop Burnham from being
OL,19,FLabour's candidate.
