OL,3,CWhy the path to Westminster is not so
OL,4,Csimple for Andy Burnham
OL,6,FIt would be a bold move from Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer and his leadership team, but
OL,8,Fas one Burnham-supporting MP told me:
OL,9,F"If they intentionally block such a
OL,10,Fpopular figure from returning as an MP
OL,11,Fwhen we are struggling in the polls
OL,12,Fjust to potentially save themselves,
OL,13,Fthey are asking for civil war." Yikes.
OL,15,FBut this is not an easy decision for
OL,16,FBurnham in any case. He will need to
OL,17,Fresign as the mayor of Greater
OL,18,FManchester, which would trigger a very
OL,19,Fexpensive regional election for the
OL,20,FLabour Party.
