OL,3,CWhy the path to Westminster is not so
OL,4,Csimple for Andy Burnham
OL,6,FHe will then, if selected, stand in a
OL,7,Fseat which both Reform and the Greens
OL,8,Fhave their eyes on. Given how
OL,9,Funpredictable by-elections are, there
OL,10,Fis no guarantee he would win.
OL,12,FAlongside Burnham, there are two other
OL,13,Fwell-known figures who are not in
OL,14,FWestminster at the moment who might
OL,15,Fhave their eyes on the seat.
OL,17,FReform's Zia Yusuf and the Green Party
OL,18,Fleader Zack Polanski are active
OL,19,Fcampaigners who are not MPs, and they
OL,20,Ftoo might be eyeing the by-election as
OL,21,Fa route into Westminster.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
