OL,3,CWhy the path to Westminster is not so
OL,4,Csimple for Andy Burnham
OL,6,FNo one has made their position clear
OL,7,Fyet, but expect the Gorton and Denton
OL,8,Fby-election to be a tough battle,
OL,9,Fespecially if there are three major
OL,10,Fpolitical figures all running.
OL,12,FNow even if (and there are a lot of
OL,13,Fvariables here) Burnham threw his hat
OL,14,Finto the ring, even if he got the
OL,15,Fselection and then even if he went on
OL,16,Fto win the seat, he still has a long
OL,17,Fpath to becoming leader - if that is
OL,18,Fsomething he really wants.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
