OL,3,CWhy the path to Westminster is not so
OL,4,Csimple for Andy Burnham
OL,6,FHe will need to gather support within
OL,7,Fthe Labour Party, get a large number
OL,8,Fof MPs on side, challenge the PM and
OL,9,Fbeat other potential leadership
OL,10,Fcandidates.
OL,12,FIt is a long road, it's all highly
OL,13,Fspeculative - but for now, one of the
OL,14,Ffirst steps on that journey has
OL,15,Fpotentially opened up.
